sequenceDiagram

participant User
participant OrderService
participant BillingService
participant NotificationService

User->>OrderService: POST /orders
activate OrderService
OrderService->>BillingService: POST /billings
activate BillingService
Note left of BillingService: write off money
BillingService->>NotificationService: POST /notification
activate NotificationService
NotificationService->>BillingService: 200 OK
deactivate NotificationService
BillingService->>OrderService: 202 ACCEPTED/400 BAD REQUEST
deactivate BillingService
OrderService->>User: 201 CREATED/400 BAD REQUEST
deactivate OrderService
